Package ru.nsu.cjvth

Class Tree<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nsu.cjvth.Tree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - type of the elements
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Tree<E>>
    public class Tree<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Tree<E>>
    Tree data structure. Supports adding and removing child nodes, iterating. Descendants are accessible through references. Every node has a value.
